thread.title: Marissa

author: Marissa
title: Marissa
text: Check in location confusing. Parking spaces unlabeled, a rude note was left on my car and was threatened the police would be called on me. Rude check in personnel. Incorrect information on key check outs were written down, leading to confusing check out. No response when I needed to check in early and call center unable and unwilling to connect me directly to staff at the place.
